{"tid":1306374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葉劉淑儀：田北俊是惡意攻擊","createTime":"2019-07-11T06:31:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T07:03:32.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2a3c54c368e5b88993634f7dbd9529ea6f6e8f43","tid":1306374,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T06:31:03.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】一批市民集會支持警隊執法及多名行政會議成員留任。<br />\n<br />\n行政會議成員葉劉淑儀到警察總部接收他們的信件。<br />\n<br />\n這批人士自稱為市民自發群組，他們支持警方嚴厲執法，認為近期部分的公眾集會擾亂公眾秩序，要求警方不要發出不反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n他們又批評自由黨榮譽主席田北俊的言論，點名支持幾名行會成員，認為他們真實地反映了民意，葉劉淑儀亦批評田北俊是惡意攻擊。"},{"pid":"723b28f00e8a0d434a8916e598fd572b2f9fc543","tid":1306374,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T06:31:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=355027\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D355027&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt852xR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=ef18448f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D355027&h=61094df0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=355027</a>"},{"pid":"4949b54cbf2219503750059018a49a6c1ad46b78","tid":1306374,"uid":273703,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T06:31:49.000Z","msg":"大家落曬注未，買定離手"},{"pid":"bd9328ff6b0e96e7e6e91149a3840080c080b8ae","tid":1306374,"uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T06:31:58.000Z","msg":"玻璃淑儀"},{"pid":"2f0e3c0486a0b9ef1ab544f07cb55b3b8baab7fd","tid":1306374,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T06:32:19.000Z","msg":"碎滿一地"},{"pid":"08ad297b18b7d1fa72cb322f2a6264379cf64a57","tid":1306374,"uid":254371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T06:32:30.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmo